programme.title: YE ISHQ SAMAJH NA AYE
programme.desc: 'Ye Ishq Samaj Na Aye' delves into the story of Rida and Hassan, a devoted couple who firmly believe in the invincibility of their love, unwavering against any storm that may come their way. However, their steadfast belief is put to the test when they find themselves unable to confront the slightest hint of doubt creeping into their hearts. What begins as a mere spark soon engulfs them in flames, consuming the fortress of their love in its fiery wake, leaving nothing but ashes in its aftermath.

programme.title: SUHANA
programme.desc: A talented young woman finds herself in a conservative in-laws' home. The story revolves around her battles after her husband departs Pakistan in pursuit of better job prospects. Weighted of traditional expectations and the stifling atmosphere of her in-laws' conservatism, she battles against loneliness and suffocating environment. The story of her discovering hope within her own talents and aspirations. Determined to assert her independence and reclaim her sense of self-worth, she embarks on a courageous journey of self-discovery and empowerment.

programme.desc: In this saga, the renowned Peer, Noor Elahi, embarks on a relentless quest for a grandson, driven by obsession after his own sons reject his succession.
